\[\begin{pmatrix} -5 + 7t \\ 4 - 4t \end{pmatrix},\]for $t \in \mathbb{R}.$  Thus, $b = \boxed{-4}.$

Note that the direction vector is of the form $\begin{pmatrix} -7 \\ b \end{pmatrix}$ if and only if $b = \boxed{-4}.$

